<HEADLINE>
FT  30 JUN 93 / People: Non-executive appointments - Hammerson
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Alvin Glick is resigning from HAMMERSON.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Hammerson Property Investment and Development Corp.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
