</XX>
<CO>British Bio-Technology Group.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P2834 Pharmaceutical Preparations.
</IN>
<XX>
