    P9721 International Affairs.
    P4911 Electric Services.
    P1311 Crude Petroleum and Natural Gas.
    P4813 Telephone Communications, Ex Radio.
    P1611 Highway and Street Construction.
    P1629 Heavy Construction, NEC.
</IN>
